oad/v0.1.1/go-find-archived-gh-actions_Windows_x86_64.zip.sigstore.json"}],"body":"## Changelog\n### New Features\n* b4d0daab2cf283713c8ac100d9f6bfa36017db70: feat: check specific directory or multiple repos in a base-dir for workflow files to scan (@toozej)\n* 965e2bd7a0a8ad0d24eaaff1cb7946babcd3288a: feat: github API concurrency, version caching, fix major version pin comparison, stale CLI flag (@toozej)\n* 3dba59391f3486900cb752baff62d30f71340878: feat: swap to using go-github library for GH issue handling (@toozej)\n### Bug fixes\n* 4d238be28a45e63fc49581dd41d21e0c9e6992de: fix(ci): skip nfpm, brew, and sign pipes in weekly-docker-refresh workflow (@toozej)\n### Other work\n* 3a3da68b50e80a2354621d190a347aa79ff768c5: Update Node.js feature version in devcontainer.json (@toozej)\n* 3d4a07f11495124527a377f976616af81a4c0d90: goreleaser updates for cosign v3 (@toozej)\n* 9b6ba92856f3dbe4ca28123e011fd9c073143a0d: update deps (@toozej)\n* 375adaf84d1d1405729e609109b3a6ef23904e54: update deps (@toozej)\n* f2043a08ce48facbe3fc7615f62f901494c50fcd: update: Makefile and Dockerfiles for Debian Trixie and standardization (@toozej)\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/toozej/go-find-archived-gh-actions/compare/v0.1.0...v0.1.1\n\n","createdAt":"2026-05-08T22:48:11Z","isDraft":false,"isPrerelease":false,"name":"v0.1.1","publishedAt":"2026-05-08T23:08:26Z","tagName":"v0.1.1","url":"https://github.com/toozej/go-sort-out-gh-actions/releases/tag/v0.1.1"}
